 from the overdense meteor train boundary through fast,\ntemperature independent, dissociative recombination governed by the second\nDamkohler number. Possible implications for trail diffusion and lifetimes are\ndiscussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Apr 2017 16:45:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Apr 2017 17:54:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-14"}
