alue\nof $H_0$ than $\\Lambda$CDM, therefore in better agreement with local\nmeasurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Apr 2017 11:16:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Oct 2017 14:22:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-25"}
